  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>모든 인쇄물</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24523df5-254f-4e16-be24-c703c6c02d16\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a3cd5f1a-77a1-48ca-94ef-7fb910a0640f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fc378dca-000e-4ed8-9d6b-011df2bfb38f\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>진심</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-412a281c-16c5-421f-b445-37d6cc97384f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMjQx/MDAxNzQxMzk3NjI2MTgy.OhaCJVAGpIgjlcfx10tKlT3qmJWNeivq3IQxWxmr59Ag.-UKMRUWtWyPof9bW7qoCzo-_s-CnSMytS02nMv-baC4g.PNG/Label_Tag_Mockup_3.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"4000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMjQx/MDAxNzQxMzk3NjI2MTgy.OhaCJVAGpIgjlcfx10tKlT3qmJWNeivq3IQxWxmr59Ag.-UKMRUWtWyPof9bW7qoCzo-_s-CnSMytS02nMv-baC4g.PNG/Label_Tag_Mockup_3.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">사각 행택은 재단으로 작업할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>택(Tag)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a57cec74-1276-4799-bc79-31936b65d833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 의류나 기타 용품에 부자재로 사용되는 종이 설명서(?) 같은 상품입니다. 이 택에는 가격을 나열할 수도 있고 제품의 설명이 들어갈 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9993a53f-fb8f-4746-aad8-56ed65818776\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2852bdc2-ce87-42ff-a681-86b74d9d8f4f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75111a05-d562-486a-920e-f1790c128db8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-453dc61d-9d10-4c95-b68e-4d060a4d7f25\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종류는 크게 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-222bf1d0-141c-4c74-8789-6a6459e3a512\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>행택</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d16df872-aed5-4daa-86ce-1a9c807535ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">과 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b6c9c053-7bf9-4136-879a-4e08ec2ae423\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>헤더택</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-890cab31-d801-4645-be16-49a19d1473ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">으로 구별됩니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b453558f-c8a3-494b-9ae9-ab1eea1b1a97\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>행택</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d12e974-6ae4-49c3-a168-72ee5949505c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 실이나 투명한 스트링으로 묶어서 사용되는 것이고 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e9c96496-a926-429f-ad01-783836ebaa81\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>헤더택</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e584dca-96d4-475f-93ce-f5716c5bfbd8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 비닐 등의 포장재를 위에 스테이플러 등으로 고정하여 제작되는 제품입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-823edbae-1b3e-4f45-9cf2-8742b72281f8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-278f2eb4-ceb0-4d38-94cf-89c8d477c457\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-468e3132-978e-475a-be72-8b9f817ec7a4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e6e9dfdf-020f-4dab-85ec-bdb98e7b7192\" style=\"color:#555555;\">일단 곡선이나 자유형이 아닌 사각형은 재단을 하고 타공으로 제작될 수 있습니다. 다만</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f842efe4-a8cd-4222-a6fa-6f8ed192d2fc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\"> 재단은 도무송(톰슨)보다는 오차가 발생될 수 있어 삐뚤게 재단되어 사고로 이어지는 경우가 많으니 주의</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8c76538a-0470-4c18-b16f-19a6d7aaf0be\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a599f0ea-f8a1-4100-8fc5-4f3d22b54206\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3b86566-c182-4d17-9600-90021d9c14b7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a4ff0975-5021-4a0a-b888-96eb818d5d3c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24d2ba77-b3d1-4fc5-a69e-6fdb0d1750de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇다고 하더라도 재단으로 제작이 되면 도무송(톰슨)보다 가장 경제적으로 제작될 수 있습니다. 그러면 어떤 경우에 재단으로 가능할까요? 다음과 같은 경우 재단으로 제작하시기를 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b84dc703-8577-40c4-87cb-a68a52e3f4a9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ff443f5f-5ba4-44f1-9c46-0b817e3a583d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db3d830e-c2fe-4c62-8732-44a5e45407d8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3ca98c4b-9758-4b2c-b114-1ff9995792cd\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>재단으로 가능한 경우</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17bf4c13-19c5-4d4d-b7dc-3e9a04ec39a5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-19578bec-b478-47b4-9811-aad6b8f9d9f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인이 약간의 삐뚤어짐이 허용되는 상황</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dd29768f-ca5d-4ed9-b10b-d2988c0b454b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-074f48ff-3bfa-4d4f-8465-e5aba3f309e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">예를 들어 다음의 경우라면 재단으로 제작이 돼도 크게 상관이 없을 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aea8fd9d-8a17-4042-bdaa-710c83f3f6e0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f1570adc-71cb-4b89-9306-49405f940996\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f81b85f2-dc31-4f93-b040-c0c845cdcf0c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eb5f4226-f5b4-4c35-a18c-f43a3957056e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">파란선</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bca688f6-b7bf-4a61-8c31-22e9ece37ef6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 작업선, </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b634aa34-cc59-4cdc-a670-9fc710241e99\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">빨간선</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-61c9ba3b-0f6e-4ea1-87c3-4187900cbfa5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 재단되는 선입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-521b42e4-1610-4f16-9cdc-4791b647a0f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-521b42e4-1610-4f16-9cdc-4791b647a0f5\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMTE1/MDAxNzQxNDAyMDAxNjE1.j1jIWQ89r77m8n4WGZ8EIfcPX673m6v4ObMvZlyYfWkg.2Ct_WKVcUvlHIbBhnS3WkfM68RBNwBuoxDAz_bCasNYg.PNG/1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1090\", \"originalHeight\" : \"499\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMTE1/MDAxNzQxNDAyMDAxNjE1.j1jIWQ89r77m8n4WGZ8EIfcPX673m6v4ObMvZlyYfWkg.2Ct_WKVcUvlHIbBhnS3WkfM68RBNwBuoxDAz_bCasNYg.PNG/1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-15b16d8e-7ae5-4936-a690-f42d3495cad5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-15b16d8e-7ae5-4936-a690-f42d3495cad5\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMTgx/MDAxNzQxMzk4NjM4OTMz.9pvKJQA-YjEhH-vNaqyM5K-64watOQ0p43pCsWj7Qqcg.xFqDoITfItnMjTF5xXouUnLb9W4dXsS6IPjgf2p1n9Mg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1034\", \"originalHeight\" : \"653\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMTgx/MDAxNzQxMzk4NjM4OTMz.9pvKJQA-YjEhH-vNaqyM5K-64watOQ0p43pCsWj7Qqcg.xFqDoITfItnMjTF5xXouUnLb9W4dXsS6IPjgf2p1n9Mg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-261be7be-c639-48f6-af91-955ddec89635\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d9be3903-cd61-4cf6-b3a3-e5226afe2bba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d3885f1-cba1-4d66-9d20-0340f5c525fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위의 디자인이라면 약 1mm의 재단 오차가 발생하더라도 큰 게 잘못된 것을 못 느낄 수 있습니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f1406bc1-3b4d-4979-95d6-581f8007fe0a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">물론 이 부분도 고객님의 판단에 의존하는 경우가 많겠지만 심하게 재단의 오차가 발생되지 않는다면 재단으로 제작하여 경제적인 이득을 취함이 좋은 선택일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65ba0226-6902-42f2-8a86-16a1250f96e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ff7586f0-62ee-43b6-a9a9-39f2d8ef527d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">택은 기본적으로 원가에 속해 있고 한번 읽고 버리는 소모품적인 성격이 강하므로 원가를 고려한다면 재단으로 이상이 없는 디자인으로 작업하십시오. 디자인을 재단 고려하여 잘했을 경우에 해당됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2a2c16be-334f-4351-9011-7a442071cfd4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7e636ddc-7a3a-4831-beea-9e2c30c607ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75be3897-0cc2-4d56-8875-33513ad98fa1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9c182b90-5a2d-440d-a209-56fadaf6604c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 다음의 다자인 경우라면 반드시 도무송으로 작업해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc678ca4-817a-4df6-89c1-9c41ac47b56b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-bc678ca4-817a-4df6-89c1-9c41ac47b56b\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMjUx/MDAxNzQxMzk4OTY1MTEx.ehHE5RrfDciWMeTgyTKu9WQl_qwy7mTH8p2oroXZuYsg.s7pmqtbDxjKgGxkvSNU6x3Y3sO6leCXyFWG5m7lRo04g.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1146\", \"originalHeight\" : \"695\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMjUx/MDAxNzQxMzk4OTY1MTEx.ehHE5RrfDciWMeTgyTKu9WQl_qwy7mTH8p2oroXZuYsg.s7pmqtbDxjKgGxkvSNU6x3Y3sO6leCXyFWG5m7lRo04g.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-68340181-4dd1-41eb-9f50-f41f8cf34bd1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1d56eac3-5287-4372-93b5-52e629ca3b49\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ca39dee-b702-4990-a2f2-3511956a4b4a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인을 사각 박스나 이런 문양을 넣었다면 재단의 오차가 아래와 같이 더 삐뚤게 보일 수 있습니다. 이런 디자인은 반드시 도무송(톰슨)으로 작업해서 오차를 줄여야 사고가 나지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18039986-2583-41cc-8124-e3fc623e178b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:807px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-18039986-2583-41cc-8124-e3fc623e178b\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMTAz/MDAxNzQxMzk5MTM0NDQy.ZXS7ZQ2sIiKIHnLI9cEhKPFagjKQV8vbovYdPv6uGiQg.svLy3gNHrtOIMGIRmtcpPsDwAu4ZDV71D71qTQVzc7gg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"807\", \"originalHeight\" : \"684\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMTAz/MDAxNzQxMzk5MTM0NDQy.ZXS7ZQ2sIiKIHnLI9cEhKPFagjKQV8vbovYdPv6uGiQg.svLy3gNHrtOIMGIRmtcpPsDwAu4ZDV71D71qTQVzc7gg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3fe8cd10-c530-4172-93de-40344143621a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7375ca2b-34c6-43e5-89f4-964b95134f37\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-426e8d04-118e-49e2-8d7b-a4a23381fe8d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">위, 아래가 1mm만 안 맞아도 디자인상 크게 잘못된 것처럼 보입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f7f445c6-1b3f-4ad5-b062-50a4abbd6e4a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e10ce8d4-595a-4c4a-8261-6a45c1c046df\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c9f9986-c324-436c-b610-ceca7e309555\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-852d709a-ef89-49da-ad71-926e51ee6a31\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>소모품용으로 원가가 가장 중요한 경우</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f075766-481d-4659-8303-8599c43a5fbf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f216bf3-dd26-4691-b25d-f444d9d8a197\" style=\"color:#555555;\">미리 말씀드렸지만 택(Tag)은 원가에 들어갑니다. 그렇기에 단가를 줄이는 것은 정말 중요합니다. 하지만 경우에 따라 원가보다도 제품의 품격을 살리고 또는 디자인 요소의 한 부분으로서의 역할이 강조될 수 있습니다. 이런 경우는 모양으로 디자인을 가장 많이 하십니다. 모양은 기본형이 있기는 하지만 자유롭게도 가능하니 참고하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c52716cb-1f8c-44e4-b55f-fddf729f03bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-89e087ae-3124-436a-a935-40f16bff571b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2dfdd50-64c9-4625-a857-ccb29cedd2f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b1053f8-c06c-456b-b57c-80e4456459e0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본형으로는 반원이나 위쪽 육각, 또는 물방울형 등이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0c6708a0-1204-479c-904a-7ca7964191ff\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0c6708a0-1204-479c-904a-7ca7964191ff\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMjMw/MDAxNzQxMzk5ODk3NzEx.0APIgxwDbaw1bCc67GpTjGmuxFRBU4HKaBhShZ4sjH0g.Aqs1b6NMxybsMe7QchC-W44X43AMa_tdYKhgzkvq_i8g.PNG/1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3544\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1182\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMjMw/MDAxNzQxMzk5ODk3NzEx.0APIgxwDbaw1bCc67GpTjGmuxFRBU4HKaBhShZ4sjH0g.Aqs1b6NMxybsMe7QchC-W44X43AMa_tdYKhgzkvq_i8g.PNG/1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1ce3b584-2284-48ac-97a6-fa9ac4e7dc27\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7964b3be-c52e-4bda-bc86-de009b302ac2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6fd92fc6-0c83-42d9-8493-c02c9018a5db\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>하지만 원가를 고려한 사각형이라면 재단과 타공으로 주문하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-03d1650a-2e3c-46a8-922b-407bcf7e10c8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56d7b0f0-9a30-4d3e-a9e4-bf50d4821a86\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-06ffaefc-ace4-479e-af2b-be0f4fa6343f\" style=\"\">가장 경제적인 주문사양</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d0e2b0b7-0e24-4037-bcd0-5f569ad3d2b2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a71f76a-2277-4a8f-aa78-51ad6f41ef18\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-031c93fb-e52f-43c6-a2bb-d7afcc62885a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">원가를 고려한 가장 경제적인 주문사항을 알려드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-045018f8-04b6-43b3-8bbc-245a8ead0857\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-732b97e2-710e-47dd-a9a7-247dd5c40877\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-31a1ccd6-b4d1-450f-8e7b-4caefa78cb7c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-adf5fd63-7811-46bf-9139-71180fe1c77b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a118a127-abda-4c0a-a921-a7d3750f946c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 양면 무광코팅지 250g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de13ca5b-a578-48d0-94ba-76381a9b3ee3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-37b4951b-b288-4512-b64a-d7c0e79c6bba\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1057c57a-d06d-4e39-b09e-69ea45dcfa7d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 90mm × 50mm</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-770f8de3-5265-463e-b4cb-f76b7df91dc5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c8979724-0dcc-4e4d-96cf-351aa75f6cd3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1e3fbeb-2401-4806-99dd-603584d05a83\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 양면 칼라 8도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a173681-e5ac-4372-92f1-7e0bf3ff5ff0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fb9b5e4c-9d06-4a9b-b49d-a43bc0912d94\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-198f0bef-16ec-41c7-8ed9-4c6a8d6f5d91\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 사각 재단</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-05da0e2a-c85e-4083-aebd-f9ef2725a9d2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7e75bf62-f234-4a1e-b299-54597fac2f34\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0623933c-5076-41d0-8618-7f45a34eeacb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 상단 타공 1개</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-37e81a0e-d93c-4835-80d3-28640e766344\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-43af4057-e4bf-4f15-be8c-b6d1fc637b31\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ce1d522f-4b79-4d55-b106-7fc5926ba962\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 500개</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-197fde3b-38e8-4309-a949-e9a85100cc62\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2864d424-9cda-4428-9c87-aa98a698d343\" style=\"color:#555555;\">-------------------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1bed305f-d496-4af7-9e51-c29f603ffa78\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f32da533-9ebc-45d9-8b51-b8b9de23d2fc\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>단가 : 18,000원부터 ~</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3d3f261a-67d5-40d4-93b5-40ce6303a436\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-87bae8a2-464b-43d8-a098-ef54b3675e5b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(부가세 /택배비 별도 : 500장 주문시 약 택배비는 3,000원정도 나옵니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f05753d1-3d02-4100-bc6f-501066869b1e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f29ad2db-ab72-4ff3-8fed-a10423a09ab9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3dcc9978-e19d-4e86-9d84-11b394667a28\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e1f99da7-d0b1-417c-8d40-a944489d2030\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1260a5ac-e47e-4757-ab1b-a304bf45936a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 다량이나 다수 건수 주문 시 무료 디자인 이벤트 (전화문의)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f2b3ba0-cbbb-4715-8209-7e154cb3e0ce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1d58d014-8b55-4f28-af79-c20b4158b6f4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사각 재단을 고려한 디자인으로 제작됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cf352678-d1e2-4097-8b08-6971724eda61\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f9622424-4ba1-407a-8387-93b9a163fac5\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-b1e637c9-75c8-4166-a17f-c128cd4f44f8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98c38e71-03d4-407f-a304-42a6bbe74d0b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5466bf78-4253-49d6-91d7-06782b9cc494\" style=\"\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 추천하는 사양</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-44f433bf-ae17-44f8-8e3f-a2cb8acc3ce2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c41bb1d-8a54-4431-9ff2-36ea95ab3377\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d4d2a5f4-3366-472a-97e6-c059c0be7637\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 자신 있게 추천합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47d15e7f-0a4a-4c2c-963c-151f2af15610\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2754b10c-cace-4c65-82fe-bcbb27f5b9f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0a1c45f4-5f78-4a0f-8a83-8c4d0211e5f8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-531ed822-6df5-48af-85a4-ac71c3975c5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-93f15f8c-2de2-495e-aaa5-2acbb598efeb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 수입지 약 250g 내외 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-77aa4c6f-dcf8-409a-9c5a-ebff706a502e\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(반누브, 아르떼 등)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ac62c61-9dee-4b27-93f6-b5783bc5986b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b619294-3b19-45f4-af64-79098d3a6736\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-46fa9f40-2d4d-476a-8486-0f4ad5b5e79f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 사각 재단 + </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f360fc1e-90a3-4bd3-9802-5cda1c5c3025\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>라운드(귀돌이) 추가</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba4448bd-aefe-416a-a2fa-6f8d81ae26f2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c8ac6be1-ceff-4efb-866b-787326c1b55b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3547e81a-821b-49f7-8cf2-25339721788f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a509f856-5561-4da6-a6cc-41bce59cb6bf\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>로고 박인쇄 추가</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-159c6e46-a774-4b78-9f7e-1808f5bc9a8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-390ab3f1-80bb-4029-a31d-1d851343eaa7\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-9af323c6-769b-425c-976f-5a4a7e8d3861\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0cf2163c-2d10-4a75-b182-dc923914a488\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b38b9c7e-2ce3-40fe-bfa9-e93ae13ae105\" style=\"\">재작업이 안되는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c2ead530-0f44-4a98-a8b4-8be23e4e59c1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6584b2e7-2e3a-496d-a4a9-2cfe9e849a83\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c94fc768-52ce-4587-b0c0-821f2bd61b2e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 항상 고객의 입장에서 생각합니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-34d33ba6-f88f-4933-a28b-6c0252c4edba\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 상담을 통해 재단의 위험성(?)을 인지 시켜 드렸음에도 불구하고 약간의 재단 오차로 인한 재작업은 불가능합니다. 이점 양해하여 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4373f1a2-c1df-4f08-896f-ff9e460e0fa0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99e190cc-a02e-4b08-b0e0-48e80d93644b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e8565dc-1537-494b-a15c-8e42ee4041d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-654bacf1-e5b9-4103-bd4f-c152b1d37f8f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>재작업이 안되는 경우</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5b60e7c5-8cae-4823-b933-f51f00a75a12\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 재단 오차는 1~2mm가 발생될 수 있습니다. 이점을 이해하고도 주문하시면 재작업을 해드릴 수가 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e27cc1f2-1174-4b70-8586-0e5aea15c1a0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-37879980-56c7-4808-85a3-1e2450357a14\" style=\"color:#555555;\">타공의 위치도 약간은 이격이 발생됩니다. 하지만 이 부분은 크지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c353604-9529-4438-93da-3a8b52e7e366\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c65efb58-84af-41a0-af63-1f45d9f586f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-38bab43a-2a63-41e2-a227-1b3c26e2e61c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-17824403-4389-486b-8def-961ed5a51a6c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 디자인 파일을 접수하면 디자인 상태에 따라 도무송으로 제작해야 할지 아니면 재단도 무난할지 아니면 다른 코팅이 없는 재단으로 처리할지를 상담 드립니다. 코팅을 하면 재단 밀림이 더 발생할 수 있기 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-754dd219-01ee-4932-9f0a-cc47410cefec\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9f80ef97-2e18-40b3-ae5e-b83d7d8faa11\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-897c51d4-7694-42b7-8e4e-ff09e4b39a7a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-70119f65-4061-469e-805f-57284eae2938\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\"><b>반드시 주문 전에 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하여 주문하시기 바랍니다. 고객의 입장에서 친절하게 상담을 드리겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-446d985c-9527-4154-b7c0-fdf82b5e5b90\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-446d985c-9527-4154-b7c0-fdf82b5e5b90\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMTY5/MDAxNzQxNDAxODY2OTAy.69jK4fmZWNxF1C88iWXNpV5Fttaug5tYTxWogjkhRngg.fmghBmoBuK4IyMRRSbLVU8Jr2nlw3tVCRiE4KgbwcNkg.PNG/Label_Tag_Mockup_2.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"4000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMDhfMTY5/MDAxNzQxNDAxODY2OTAy.69jK4fmZWNxF1C88iWXNpV5Fttaug5tYTxWogjkhRngg.fmghBmoBuK4IyMRRSbLVU8Jr2nlw3tVCRiE4KgbwcNkg.PNG/Label_Tag_Mockup_2.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223788486637#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\